## Fallback UI Patterns

Custom Fallback Component:

function MyFallback({ errorId, onReset }) {
  return (
    <div className="error-page">
      <h1>Oops! Something broke.</h1>
      <p>Error reference: <strong>{errorId}</strong></p>
      <button onClick={onReset}>Reload section</button>
      <a href="/">Go to homepage</a>
    </div>
  );
}

Inline (for non-critical components):

<ErrorBoundary fallback={() => <span style={{ color: 'gray' }}>Widget unavailable</span>}>
  <RecommendationWidget />
</ErrorBoundary>

